				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"><br><br>Stick with <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Nektulos Forest</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->.<br><br>You have started here and right now is not the time to be traveling, wasting time running about.  You want levels, and you want them fast.<br><br>The fun part about leveling to 4 is that you now have your first pet.  Your pet is not the toughest melee machine you've ever seen, but your Earth pet will do a fairly decent job. <br><br>Keep yourself alive by making sure you have Gate memmed at all times.<br><br>But death is not a big concern.  Spells to mem are really just Earth pet, Burn, and Gate.   Summon pet a Dagger and send him out.  You will still be doing a lot of Melee'ing with your pet at this point to keep him alive.  <br><br>But look for blue mobs around the Nektulos Forest Newbie Log.  You should find plenty of yard trash to keep you moving ahead.<br><br>Before you know it, you'll be 7 and and you could then start trying to take the magicians and chanters that are around the Wizard Portal.  These are still gonna be very tough, but if you can single out the front one, you might get lucky.  <br><br>The port book for PoK is right near there, it's closer then the Neriak zone so if you want to run there to get away, it's a pretty safe spot.  <br><br>However, you probably just want to stay around the Newbie Log and around the path near there till you hit 8.<br><br>These levels are gonna breeze by here.  The EQ changes have made leveling to level 10 trivial so don't stress too heavily on these.  They're easy.<br><br>Good Luck!  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile" border="0" /> --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT="<img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile" border="0" />"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>Kastin Spellz<br> -- &quot;...with great power, comes great responibility&quot; <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START <img src="images/smiles/icon_biggrin.gif" alt="icon_biggrin" border="0" /> --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT="<img src="images/smiles/icon_biggrin.gif" alt="icon_biggrin" border="0" />"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
